title: How to Execute Scripts with Delta Executor | Roblox Script Guide (2025)
transcript: copy the script from our website which is given in description then go to Delta executor game in which you want to execute script click on Delta icon now click on home icon then click on upload button now give the name to your script in title bar and paste the script in script bar then click on ADD script now you can execute the script by clicking on execute button and enhance your Roblox experience s
